TAKASABURO SEKINO et al. v. Tom C. CLARK et al. No. 3517. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Sept. 13, 1948. A. L. Wirin and Fred Okrand, both of Los Angeles, Cal., and Warwick C. Lamoreaux, of Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellants. Dan B. Shields, U. S. Atty., and Scott M. Matheson and O. K. Clay, Asst. U. S. Atty., all of Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellee.

Before BRATTON, HUXMAN, and MURRAH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellants.
